<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>A is the only where the equal groups aren't in a straight line.</li>
      <li>B is the only where the equal groups and the dots in the equal groups aren’t always right next to one another.</li>
      <li>C is the only one where the equal groups are not organized in rows.</li>
      <li>D is the only one that doesn't have 15 dots.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


